a-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKdAqEQH.png&h=9b40f637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>727元朗集中反黑</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">香港人絕不向黑勢力低頭！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但係！記住！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求！缺！一！不！可！<br />\n香港人！不！撤！不！散！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>義士不是condom！<br />\n說好的一個都不能少！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/01iorVB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F01iorVB.png&h=b7815076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑警於721，無人衝擊、毫無預警下<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>開槍</strong></span></span>！<br />\n總共開咗<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">36槍！</span></span><br />\n<em><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係開槍！唔係扔彈呀！</span></strong></em><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>如果呢啖氣你都忍到嘅話，咁6月12號仲平乜撚嘢反？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求！</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n二、釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n三、撤回612暴動定性<br />\n四、追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n五、立即實行雙普選，還我真香港！</span><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W16xijK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW16xijK.png&h=9fb73358&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mXaewEN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmXaewEN.png&h=6e7eb5c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0258c5927888fd6c0b6114f541a0b21617652402","tid":1357241,"uid":227597,"like":0,